<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">3月25日下午，江西软件职业技术大学执行校长范红铭在创客中心路演大厅为江软学子们带来了一堂别开生面的“开学第一课”。他以“启航新征程、续写新辉煌”为主题，深入浅出地传达了全国全省“两会”精神，引发了同学们的深思与共鸣。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-03-29%2014%3A45%3A40IMG_0061.png?Expires=2027054741&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=tRw7kqeRcuma2rX0ED%2ByNpukWa8%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">范校长首先引导同学们深入学习贯彻全国全省</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">“两会”精神，并讲授了学校努力培养德技并修的高素质技术技能人才的“开学第一课”，他对同学们提出三点要求和希望：一要自立自强，持续谱写奋进新篇章；二要守正创新，推动强校建设稳步前进；三要技能成才，争做新时代的弄潮儿。希望同学们以“团结、勤勉、求实、拓新”精神，以信心凝聚力量、以实干谱写华章，用实际行动承担起属于我们的责任，把握好生命中“热辣滚烫”的每一分钟，书写无愧于祖国、无愧于时代的绚丽篇章，以优异成绩迎接中华人民共和国成立75周年！</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-03-29%2014%3A49%3A04IMG_0112.png?Expires=2027054945&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=Yfthp%2BoxrdnXzeOEX%2FuLJC%2FWn9E%3D" alt="" width="650" height="404" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 28pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">这堂</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">“开学第一课”站位高远、精彩生动，具有很强的亲和力与感染力，让大家进一步丰富了知识储备，开阔了眼界视野，夯实了强国有我、强校有我的责任感和使命感，坚定了对未来美好大学生活的信心。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>